source: A utility cabinet marks an area as yours. Other players can't search nearby one, unlock locks, etc. unless you give them permission or they break it down. In addition, zombies don't appear near them.<cf><cf>Press <B>{ConstructionKey}</> to open your construction menu.<cf><cf>Go to the Utility Cabinets tab. Select a utility cabinet then click Build in the left menu.<cf><cf>Place it somewhere by pressing and holding <B>{PrimaryKey}</>.

source: Select where you'd like your character to start in the world of VEIN.
Translation: 选择您希望角色在VEIN世界中的起始位置。

source: Shoes made of leather. Part of a correctional officer uniform.

source: Shoes made of leather. Part of a police uniform.

source: Shown under your server name. Add details about playstyles, rules, etc. here.

source: Skill books give one extra stat level.

source: Smaller civilian vehicles use 50% less gasoline.

source: Sold for a limited time online from a highly reputable online pharmacy for the low, low price of $399.99.<cf><cf>Claims to cure the \zombie virus\". "
Translation: 在线限时销售，来自信誉良好的在线药店，仅需399.99美元的低价。<cf><cf>声称能治愈僵尸病毒"。"

Translation: 一些章鱼烧，每个都包含一口章鱼，上面撒有鲣鱼片和蛋黄酱。

source: Some edible gold flakes. Can turn a normal meal into a boujee meal, probably.

source: Some fishing line. Useful for fishing.

source: Some food, such as canned food, won't expire for many in-game years.
Translation: 一些食物（如罐头食品）在游戏内多年内不会过期。

Translation: 一些原煤。一种有用的燃料，燃烧温度与精炼木炭一样高，但无需精炼。含有杂质使其更重。<cf><cf>然而，这种煤能进一步精炼吗？

source: Storage space for notes, schematics, and other various documents.<cf><cf>Won't fit other items.

Translation: 用于存放废料的存储空间。<cf><cf>无法容纳其他物品。

source: The UC doesn't have enough resources. Unless you add some, your structures will decay and lose health.

source: The administrative center and community gathering place for Saranac.

Translation: 萨拉纳克的行政中心和社区聚集地。

source: The air around you smells absolutely foul, almost like something is decomposing. Whatever the source, it’s only a matter of time before a horde approaches.
Translation: 你周围的空气闻起来极其恶臭，几乎像有东西在腐烂。无论源头是什么，尸群接近只是时间问题。

source: The air around you smells musty, zombies likely won’t pick up on it… yet.
Translation: 你周围的空气闻起来发霉，僵尸可能还不会注意到……暂时。

source: The air around you smells putrid, almost like rotting meat or eggs. Whatever the source, zombies will definitely notice this.
Translation: 你周围的空气闻起来腐臭，几乎像腐烂的肉或鸡蛋。无论源头是什么，僵尸肯定会注意到这个。

source: The air around you smells stinky, zombies may or may not get attracted to the area.
Translation: 你周围的空气闻起来很臭，僵尸可能会也可能不会被吸引到这个区域。

source: The amount of water in the soil. Make sure this plant has some water at all times.
Translation: 土壤中的水量。确保这株植物始终有水分。

source: The apocalypse is stressful, and you're starting to feel it. You should find a way to relax.
Translation: 末日压力很大，你开始感觉到了。你应该找个方式放松一下。

source: The area around you smells great, like perfume or flowers.
Translation: 你周围的区域闻起来很棒，像香水或花朵。

source: The area around you smells great. Maybe some fresh food?
Translation: 你周围的区域闻起来很棒。也许有新鲜食物？

Translation: 你周围的区域闻起来不错。

source: The area around you smells normal.
Translation: 你周围的区域闻起来正常。

source: The center of your base.<cf><cf>Be sure to build this in a well-guarded location - if anyone gets to it, they can claim everything in your base for themselves.
Translation: 你的基地中心。<cf><cf>确保在防守严密的位置建造这个 - 如果有人到达这里，他们可以声称你基地中的所有东西归自己所有。

source: The chair is located in front of you. How could you miss it?
Translation: 椅子就在你面前。你怎么可能错过它？

source: The chance of dirty bandages becoming infected is reduced 25%.
The chances of causing floor creaks are reduced by 50%.
Translation: 引起地板吱吱作响的几率降低50%。

source: The claws of the apocalypse is wearing down on you. You're about to snap.
Translation: 末日的魔爪正在磨损你。你快要崩溃了。

source: The corpse appears to have exploded.

source: The door is locked. You'll have to head through the window.<cf><cf>Press <B>{RaiseFistsKey}</> to raise your fists, and <B>{PrimaryKey}</> to punch the window.
Translation: 门锁着。你得从窗户进去。<cf><cf>按<B>{RaiseFistsKey}</>举起拳头，按<B>{PrimaryKey}</>击打窗户。

source: The east entrance to a huge mining complex.

source: The fire rate of ranged weapons is reduced by 15% but is more accurate.

Translation: 发电机看起来在运行！现在打开卧室里的保险丝盒。<cf><cf>VEIN中的电力、水和许多其他系统都连接到真实电网，所以如果有任何保险丝盒或接线盒关闭，电力就会中断。

source: The impact's jaw is broken and bloody. It looks like they dislocated their jaw trying to bite something.
Translation: 撞击者的下巴断裂且流血。看起来他们试图咬东西时下巴脱臼了。

source: The impact's jaw is broken and bloody. It looks like they dislocated their jaw trying to bite something.

source: The local Methodist church in Saranac. Formerly a place of refuge.

source: The negative effects of consuming cooked human flesh are reduced by 25%.

source: The one that started it all.<cf><cf>Put it in a TV to watch.
Translation: 一切开始的那个。<cf><cf>放入电视观看。

source: The only way to reduce stress is killing things.

Translation: 这个的主人要么是侦探，要么是网络论坛版主，或者两者都是。

Translation: 受害者似乎被一辆非常大的车辆碾压，由于靠近铁轨，可能是火车。

source: The victim appears to have bled out before losing consciousness and dying.
Translation: 受害者似乎在失去意识和死亡前失血过多。

source: The victim appears to have drowned to death.
The victim appears to have hit something at a high speed.
Translation: 受害者似乎高速撞到了什么东西。

source: The victim appears to have suffocated to death.
The victim died of a blunt impact.
The victim died of a large blunt impact wound.
Translation: 受害者死于大型钝器撞击伤。

source: The victim has many small lacerations on their corpse. It appears they bled to death.
Translation: 受害者的尸体上有许多小撕裂伤。看起来他们失血过多而死。

source: The victim has multiple flesh wounds which appear to be from human hands.
Translation: 受害者有多处看起来来自人手的皮肉伤。

source: The victim has multiple stab wounds on their corpse.
Translation: 受害者的尸体上有多处刺伤。

source: The victim has small stab wounds peppering their arms.
Translation: 受害者的手臂上散布着小刺伤。

source: The victim is covered in bite wounds which appear to have come from a person.
Translation: 受害者身上布满咬伤，看起来来自人类。

source: The victim is covered in severe burns, and was likely the cause of death.
Translation: 受害者身上布满严重烧伤，这可能是死因。

source: The victim is emaciated. It's likely they starved to death.
Translation: 受害者消瘦。他们很可能饿死了。

source: The victim was bleeding from the mouth. It is likely they were poisoned.
Translation: 受害者口鼻出血。他们很可能中毒了。

source: The victim's corpse appears to be dehydrated.
Translation: 受害者的尸体似乎脱水了。

source: The wastewater processing facility for Dannemora and Saranac.
Translation: 丹尼莫拉和萨拉纳克的废水处理设施。

source: The west entrance to a huge mining complex.
Translation: 大型采矿综合体的西入口。

source: There are blinds in the way.<cf><cf>Use your scroll wheel to scroll to "Up", then hold <B>{UseKey}</> to move them.
Translation: 有百叶窗挡住去路。<cf><cf>使用滚轮滚动到"向上"，然后按住<B>{UseKey}</>移动它们。

source: There are clear gunshot wounds to the victim.
Translation: 受害者身上有明显的枪伤。

source: There are electrical burns covering the victim's body.
Translation: 受害者身上布满电烧伤。

source: There aren't any traffic jams now.

source: This map does not support GPS.

This map is BlankFlatland but with world partition on and set<cf>to a small distance.<cf>The point is to test multiplayer desync.<cf><cf>There are two teleport points - 'near' and 'far'.<cf>Teleport to far, wait for stuff to unload, then teleport back.<cf><cf>The cell size is 1600 and the load range<cf>is 3000.<cf><cf>Cubes are every 1600 units.

Translation: 您的股骨现在位于腓骨应该在的位置。夹板会帮助它更快愈合。

source: Your ability to break into locked doors or containers.

Translation: 您的衣服脏了。找些新的。<cf>打开您的库存，将衬衫拖到屏幕中央的服装槽来装备新衬衫。

source: Your compass HUD will show discovered & undiscovered locations.

source: Your heart is racing and you feel pretty good.

source: Your jump height decreases the more tired you become.

您关于活动部件的知识。

Translation: 僵尸可以破坏灯和窗户。

[无线电] <无线电>{玩家名称}</>：{消息}

Translation: 确保您在锅或平底锅中烹饪食物，而不仅仅是在炉灶上。

Translation: 当容器不在您的库存中时，您无法附加锁。

Translation: 您无法更改这个锁 - 它已锁定关闭。

Translation: 您无法更改这个锁。它受到工具柜的保护。

source: You can't change the lock on this. It is protected by a Utility Cabinet.
Translation: 您无法更改这个锁。它受到工具柜的保护。

Translation: 您无法用这个点燃任何东西。确保它已打开、通电、燃烧等。

Translation: 您需要一个打火机来执行此操作。

source: If the firearm has no rounds in it, it can't be used. Load it by dragging ammo onto it or equipping it and reloading.
Translation: 如果枪支中没有子弹，则无法使用。通过将弹药拖到其上或装备它并重新加载来加载它。

Translation: 此武器使用的弹药类型。

Translation: 您需要一个打火机来点燃这个。

source: You need Fishing Bait to fish.
You retrieved the line. A fish has eaten the bait already.
Translation: 您收回了线。鱼已经吃掉了鱼饵。

Translation: 容器中没有足够的液体。

Translation: 液体的热度。一些热液体（如茶、咖啡或可可）可能会让您感觉更舒适。

Translation: 一些液体可能会腐烂或不干净。饮用这些可能会导致医疗问题。

source: You apply this to your wound - it seems to do nothing..
Translation: 您将这个应用到您的伤口上 - 似乎没有任何作用。

Translation: 您将这个应用到您的伤口上，感染了它。

Translation: 您将这个应用到您的伤口上，消毒了它。

Translation: 您无法应用这个 - 它被冻结了。

Translation: 输入要倒入的{AmountUnit}数量。{ItemName}中有{Amount}，目标中有{ReceivingAmount}的空间。

source: Decayed food can cause food poisoning and discomfort if eaten.
Translation: 腐烂的食物如果食用可能会导致食物中毒和不适。

Translation: 食物烧焦的程度。这会降低质量并让您感到不适。

source: VEIN is a passion project.<cf>It's developed for free.<cf><cf>We accept donations for server costs, but everything else is either from our own savings, or blood, sweat, and tears.<cf><cf>There are only 2 developers -<cf>one programmer and one level designer.<cf><cf>With that in mind, there are a lot of bugs right now, and many features are incomplete.<cf><cf>Please report bugs and feedback through the ESC menu ingame. We read everything.<cf><cf>Thank you for your understanding and enjoy!<cf><cf>— Kyle & Azi
Translation: VEIN是一个充满激情的项目。<cf>它是免费开发的。<cf><cf>我们接受服务器费用的捐赠，但其他所有费用要么来自我们自己的积蓄，要么来自我们的血汗和泪水。<cf><cf>只有2名开发者-<cf>一名程序员和一名关卡设计师。<cf><cf>考虑到这一点，现在有很多错误，许多功能还不完整。<cf><cf>请通过游戏内的ESC菜单报告错误和反馈。我们会阅读所有内容。<cf><cf>感谢您的理解，祝您玩得开心！<cf><cf>—凯尔和阿兹

source: VEIN is an indie project in Early Access.<cf><cf>There are only 2 developers -<cf>one programmer and one level designer.<cf><cf>With that in mind, there are a lot of bugs right now, and many features are incomplete.<cf><cf>Please report bugs and feedback through the ESC menu ingame. We read everything.<cf><cf>Thank you for your understanding and enjoy!<cf><cf>— Kyle & Azi
Translation: VEIN是一个处于抢先体验阶段的独立项目。<cf><cf>只有2名开发者-<cf>一名程序员和一名关卡设计师。<cf><cf>考虑到这一点，现在有很多错误，许多功能还不完整。<cf><cf>请通过游戏内的ESC菜单报告错误和反馈。我们会阅读所有内容。<cf><cf>感谢您的理解，祝您玩得开心！<cf><cf>—凯尔和阿兹

Translation: 来自远程源的播放被阻止。在您的游戏设置中更改此设置以观看。

source: Enter a URL. This can't play anything like YouTube, only raw video links (e.g. ending in .mp4).
Translation: 输入一个URL。这不能播放像YouTube这样的内容，只能播放原始视频链接（例如以.mp4结尾）。

source: Enter a filename relative to Vein/Content/Movies. Everyone must have the file on their PC to play media - it will not stream to other people.
Translation: 输入相对于Vein/Content/Movies的文件名。每个人都必须在PC上有该文件才能播放媒体-它不会流式传输给其他人。

source: The TV source is Live TV. Switch the source to play video files.
Translation: 电视源是直播电视。切换源以播放视频文件。

source: The TV source is cameras. Switch the source to play video files.
Translation: 电视源是摄像头。切换源以播放视频文件。

source: The TV source is video disc items. Switch the source to play video files.
Translation: 电视源是视频光盘物品。切换源以播放视频文件。

source: The utility cabinet currently has a {Multiplier}x consumption due to the weight of its items.
Translation: 工具柜由于其物品的重量，目前有{Multiplier}倍的消耗。

source: You have removed {PlayerName} from the utility cabinet.
Translation: 您已将{PlayerName}从工具柜中移除。

source: Base raiding is turned off. Join a group with the Utility Cabinet owner to join.
Translation: 基地突袭已关闭。加入工具柜所有者的组以加入。

source: Offline raid protection is turned on, and no owners are online, so you can't raid this.
Translation: 离线突袭保护已开启，且没有所有者在线上，因此您无法突袭此物。

source: You are the original owner and can't leave.
Translation: 您是原始所有者，无法离开。

source: You have been granted permissions to build here.
Translation: 您已被授予在此处建造的权限。

source: You have voluntarily left this UC.
Translation: 您已自愿离开此工具柜。

source: Enter an amount to pour in.
The vehicle is locked. Unlock it to manipulate the gas tank.
Translation: 车辆已锁定。解锁它以操作油箱。

source: There is no gas tank installed in the vehicle.
You can't mix the fluid in this with the gas tank contents.
Translation: 您不能将此物中的液体与油箱内容物混合。

source: You fill up the tank. The tank is around {Percent}% full now.
Translation: 您加满了油箱。油箱现在大约{Percent}%满。

source: You have nothing to fill from.
You have nothing to siphon into.
Translation: 您没有东西可以抽取到。

source: This vehicle has to be stopped first.
The vehicle lights are on, but the engine doesn't start.
Translation: 车辆灯亮着，但引擎无法启动。

source: The vehicle lights are on, but there's no sound from the engine.
Translation: 车辆灯亮着，但引擎没有声音。

source: There's no key in the ignition.
There's no sound from the engine.
You fail to hotwire the ignition, damaging the vehicle but protected by your {ClothingName}.
Translation: 您热启动点火装置失败，损坏了车辆但被您的{ClothingName}保护。

source: You fail to hotwire the ignition, shocking yourself and damaging the vehicle.
Translation: 您热启动点火装置失败，电击了自己并损坏了车辆。
您成功热启动了点火装置。

source: You try to hotwire the ignition, but there is no power.
Translation: 您试图热启动点火装置，但没有电源。

source: Drag a vehicle part onto this to install it.
Translation: 将车辆部件拖到此处进行安装。

source: This is too heavy for you to uninstall manually.
Translation: 这对您来说太重了，无法手动卸载。

source: You can't seem to determine the cause of death.
You mutilate the corpse into gore.
You need to enter the server password to join your friend.
Translation: 您需要输入服务器密码才能加入您的好友。

source: Use your scissors to cut their hair.
Translation: 使用您的剪刀剪他们的头发。

source: You don't have any utility item equipped to use as a flashlight.
Translation: 您没有装备任何实用物品用作手电筒。

source: You don't have any utility item equipped to use as a map.
Translation: 您没有装备任何实用物品用作地图。

source: You got a bit stressed from eating cooked food.
Translation: 您因为吃了熟食而感到有些压力。

source: You jump out at high speed and injure yourself.
Translation: 您高速跳出并伤害了自己。

source: You jump out of the vehicle at high speed and injure yourself.
Translation: 您高速跳出车辆并伤害了自己。

source: You start exercising. Move to stop.
Translation: 您开始锻炼。移动以停止。

source: Your {ItemName} broke because it got wet.
Your {ItemName} is broken, so you can't use it.
Translation: 您的{ItemName}已损坏，因此您不能使用它。

source: Your {ItemName} is broken, so you can't use it.
Translation: 您的{ItemName}已损坏，因此您不能使用它。

source: Your {ItemName} is out of power, so you can't use it. Replace the battery in your inventory.
Translation: 您的{ItemName}没电了，因此您不能使用它。在您的库存中更换电池。

source: Your {ItemName} is out of power, so you can't use it. Replace the battery in your inventory.
Translation: 您的{ItemName}没电了，因此您不能使用它。在您的库存中更换电池。

source: Your {ItemName} is turned off. Turn it on in your inventory.
Translation: 您的{ItemName}已关闭。在您的库存中打开它。

source: Your {ItemName} is turned off. Turn it on in your inventory.
Translation: 您的{ItemName}已关闭。在您的库存中打开它。

source: Your {ItemName}'s battery was drained because it got wet.
Translation: 您的{ItemName}的电池因为湿了而耗尽。
您移除了{PlayerName}的管理员权限。

source: Connection failed (your VEIN version differs from the server's).
Translation: 连接失败（您的VEIN版本与服务器不同）。

source: Connection failed. The server is outdated.
Translation: 连接失败。服务器已过时。

source: Connection failed. Your game is outdated - please update.
Translation: 连接失败。您的游戏已过时-请更新。

source: Connection timed out due to a network failure.
Translation: 由于网络故障，连接超时。

source: Couldn't start a listen server (something's wrong with VEIN!)
Translation: 无法启动监听服务器（VEIN有问题！）

source: You don't have the required authentication to join.
Translation: 您没有所需的认证来加入。

source: You failed to connect to the server.
You were banned from the server.
You were disconnected because of a saving issue.
Translation: 您因保存问题而断开连接。

source: You were disconnected because you couldn't connect as the server.
Translation: 您因无法作为服务器连接而断开连接。

source: You were disconnected because you couldn't connect to the server.
Translation: 您因无法连接到服务器而断开连接。

source: You were disconnected due to a connection failure.
Translation: 您因连接故障而断开连接。

source: You were disconnected due to a map issue.
Translation: 您因地图问题而断开连接。

source: You were disconnected due to a missing level.
Translation: 您因缺少等级而断开连接。

source: You were disconnected due to a missing package.
Translation: 您因缺少包而断开连接。

source: You were disconnected due to a missing package.
Translation: 您因缺少包而断开连接。

source: You were disconnected due to an invalid connection address.
Translation: 您因无效的连接地址而断开连接。

source: You were disconnected for using cheats.
Translation: 您因使用作弊而断开连接。

source: You were kicked from the server.
Your game's version is different from the server's version. Make sure you're up to date.
Translation: 您的游戏版本与服务器版本不同。请确保您是最新的。

source: Your save game failed to load. It's likely from a different version of VEIN.
Translation: 您的存档游戏加载失败。它可能来自不同版本的VEIN。

source: Autosaving - please do not close the game...
Translation: 自动保存中-请不要关闭游戏...

source: The planter has no soil in it.
The slot is blocked by a growing {PlantName}.
Translation: 这个槽位被正在生长的{PlantName}阻挡了。

source: The slot is blocked by another plant.
Translation: 这个槽位被另一株植物阻挡了。

source: This can't stand on its own. Build it on a door, window, etc.
Translation: 这个不能独立站立。在门、窗等上面建造它。

source: This is blocked by a nearby utility cabinet that you do not have permissions for.
Translation: 这个被附近您没有权限的工具柜阻挡了。

source: This is stuck inside something else.
Translation: 这个卡在其他东西里面了。

source: This needs to be placed on a ceiling.
Translation: 这个需要放置在天花板上。

source: This needs to be placed on a level surface.
Translation: 这个需要放置在水平表面上。

source: This needs to be placed on a wall.
This needs to be placed on natural ground.
Translation: 这个需要放置在自然地面上。

source: This needs to be placed on something specific.
Translation: 这个需要放置在特定的东西上。

source: This needs to be planted in a planter or dirt mound.
Translation: 这个需要种植在种植器或土堆中。

source: You are building in another player's jurisdiction. They will immediately get ownership of what you're building.
Translation: 您正在另一个玩家的管辖范围内建造。他们将立即获得您正在建造的东西的所有权。

source: You are missing required stats to build this.
Translation: 您缺少建造这个所需的属性。

source: You are too tired to move this. Increase your Vitality to move things easier.
Translation: 您太累了，无法移动这个。增加您的活力来更轻松地移动东西。

source: You can clean blood with a towel.
Translation: 您可以用毛巾清洁血迹。

source: You can't build on top of this.
Translation: 您不能在这个上面建造。

source: You can't move this that far. Increase your Strength to move things farther.
Translation: 您不能移动这个那么远。增加您的力量来移动更远的东西。
您不能把那个放在这里。

source: You can't place this in the air.
Translation: 您不能把这个放在空中。

source: You have built the maximum number of utility cabinets.
Translation: 您已经建造了最大数量的工具柜。

source: The ATM reads "INSUFFICIENT FUNDS - PLEASE WITHDRAW CARD". It looks like the account has no money in it.
Translation: ATM显示"资金不足-请取卡"。看起来账户里没有钱。

source: The ATM reads "OUT OF SERVICE - SORRY FOR THE INCONVENIENCE".
Translation: ATM显示"服务暂停-对造成的不便表示歉意"。

source: The code lock shocks you from failing to input the correct code.
Translation: 密码锁因输入错误密码而电击了您。

source: You drank some of the liquid.
You emptied the oil from the engine.
You extracted {Amount} of clean oil from the engine.
Translation: 您从引擎中提取了{Amount}的清洁油。

source: You extracted {Amount} of oil from the engine. It was dirty.
Translation: 您从引擎中提取了{Amount}的油。它是脏的。

source: You feel rested. Your respawn point has been set.
Translation: 您感到休息好了。您的重生点已设置。

source: You have invited them to your group.
Translation: 您已邀请他们加入您的小组。

source: You have unused perk stat points available to spend. Open the Stats menu to unlock them.
Translation: 您有未使用的技能属性点可供花费。打开属性菜单来解锁它们。

source: You successfully withdraw ${Quantity} from the ATM.
Base PvP is off. You can't damage this.
Translation: 基地PvP已关闭。您不能损坏这个。

source: Couldn't save the game. Try again later.
Translation: 无法保存游戏。请稍后再试。

source: Saving, please do not close the game...
Translation: 正在保存，请不要关闭游戏...

source: That inventory is under a Utility Cabinet that doesn't belong to you.
Translation: 那个库存属于不属于您的工具柜。

source: Use an axe or a saw to cut trees.
You can't pick this up - you're carrying too much already.
Translation: 您不能捡起这个-您已经携带太多了。

source: You can't put this away - there's no room.
Translation: 您不能收起这个-没有空间了。

source: You can't transfer anything to a Utility Cabinet that it doesn't need for base upkeep.
Translation: 您不能将任何东西转移到不需要用于基地维护的工具柜。

source: Insert some money to purchase this.
Translation: 插入一些钱来购买这个。

source: The vending machine has no power.
The vending machine reads 'OUT OF STOCK'.
You don't have the money for this. It requires ${MoneyInDollars}.
Translation: 您没有足够的钱购买这个。它需要${MoneyInDollars}。

source: How much would you like to add?
How much would you like to take?

Translation: 这可能不会有什么作用。

source: You pour the fluid through the filter.
Translation: 您将液体通过过滤器倒出。

source: You drink some of the contents.
You haven't found this yet. Find it in the wild to see more info.
Translation: 您还没有找到这个。在野外找到它以查看更多信息。

source: You can't connect this - it would create a loop.
Translation: 您不能连接这个-它会创建一个循环。

source: How much would you like to add?
How much would you like to take?
